N2  - The author discusses the perception of the ?Academy of Management Review,? stating that it is misunderstood by those who read it and submit articles to it. The author claims that the mission statement of the journal does not fit with the contents, and summarizes the statement. The author describes the changes he wishes to make while editor of the journal.
